<div class="news-title">
<h3><a href="/article/147186.php">University Ex-Employee Arrested for Spraying Bodily Fluid on Female Student’s Shorts</a></h3>
</div>
<div class="news-first-para">
<p>Police have arrested a 43-year-old former employee of Tsuda College in Kodaira, western Tokyo, on suspicion of property damage after he allegedly took a female student’s shorts from a locker and defiled them with bodily fluid. </p>
