<div class="news-title">
<h3><a href="/article/147177.php">Okinawa Court Orders Families To Pay For Police Station Damaged In Riot</a></h3>
</div>
<div class="news-first-para">
<p>The Naha District Court’s Okinawa branch has ordered a group of former youths and their parents to pay more than 4 million yen in damages to Okinawa Prefecture over a riot that took place three years ago when a crowd surrounded the Okinawa Police Station and destroyed vehicles and other property. </p>
