<h3><a href="/article/147174.php">Over 40,000 Sign Petition Against Hotel in Wasabi Fields</a></h3>
</div>
<div class="news-first-para">
<p>A hotel construction plan in the rural wasabi-growing area of Azumino City, Nagano Prefecture, has sparked strong opposition from local residents who fear it will damage the landscape and threaten the region’s iconic wasabi fields. </p>
